locality: Madagascar. Prov. Fianarantsoa. Andringitra mountains S of Fianarantsoa. Northern part of the National Park.
Andringitra mountains S of Fianarantsoa. Northern pat of National Park. Wet meadow along the stream of river Zomandao.
Madagascar, Antananarivo Province, Vakinankaratra Region, Antsirabe District, Commune Sahanivotry, Fokontany Maromanana.
On Route Nationale 7 between Ambositra and Fianarantsoa, ca. 10 km N of Ambohimahasoa.

Itremo massif, W of Ambatofinandrahana. Along Ambalarangolana creek, ca. 1 km NNE of bridge on road to Col d'Itremo. Open areas above creek. Collected with G.E. Schatz, T. Andriamihajarivo, C. Hong-Wa, S. Rapanarivo & H. Rabarison.
